additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: WAX STRIPS Ingredients: Hydrogenated Styrene/Methyl Styrene/Indene Copolymer, Paraffinum Liquidum, Silica, Polyethylene, Parfum, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Limonene, Cl 77891, Cl 15850. WIPES Ingredients: Paraffinum Liquidum, Hexyldecyl Stearate, Parfum, Tocopheryl Acetate, Limonene.

additionalProperty.name: Contains
additionalProperty.value: 40 wax strips, 4 perfect finish wipes. Enough for 2 depilations of both half legs.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. - Retain outer pack. Read and follow all precautions and directions before use. - Suitable for use on the legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. - NOT SUITABLE for use on head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples or any other body parts. - Do not use on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated, sunburnt skin or on skin that has had an adverse reaction to waxes in the past. Always leave 72 hours between hair removal sessions.
